
Competencies

There are many ways to implement user authentication with Rails, one of the easiest is by using the Devise Gem
Devise uses its own generators to generate views, models, and migrations for models requiring registrations and passwords
Devise will also encrypt passwords automatically
Devise also comes bundled with a bunch of helper functions to make authentication easier, read about all of them in the documentation

Applications
Implement user authentication in Rails applications


Resources:
https://github.com/plataformatec/devise
